Outline to first draft with AI assist

:PATH
Outline Phase
Use AI to brainstorm structure, chapter beats, and character arcs before writing a single scene.

:PATH
Draft Phase
Generate rough scene drafts using your outline as a prompt. Edit and expand to match your voice.

:PATH
Edit Phase
Run targeted editing passes: tighten dialogue, fix pacing, check consistency across chapters.

:CHECKLIST
Novel AI Workflow Setup
[ ] Choose your primary AI writing tool
[ ] Define story premise and genre
[ ] Generate three-act outline with AI
[ ] Create character profiles
[ ] Draft chapter one with AI assist
[ ] Set daily word count target

:NOTE
Keep a style guide document. Paste it into every AI session so the model understands your tone, vocabulary preferences, and narrative voice before generating anything.

